There are two candidate CDs. 
 The positive CD has the following information: The Wall — theatrical double‑album with piano leitmotifs, cohesive sequencing and lyric‑driven narrative; warm analogue reissue retains room, microdynamics and headroom. Centered, intelligible lead vocals, restrained synths/orchestration and lush harmonies serve expansive drama—ideal for listeners favoring cinematic concept records.. 
